
********************************************************************************
* Sparx Redistributables README                                                *
*==============================================================================*
* -- log4j.jar belongs in your application's WEB-INF/lib directory. DO NOT try *
*    to share the log4j.jar file across applications (you will get sporadic    *
*    ClassCast exceptions).                                                    *
*                                                                              *
* -- If you would like to share common libraries across multiple web apps,     *
*    all files EXCEPT log4j.jar, servlet.jar and jdbc.jar may be placed into   *
*    the application server's lib directory. Usually, servlet.jar and jdbc.jar *
*    are already present in the app server's classpath and are provided in the *
*    Sparx redists only to run Ant build files from the command line.          *
*                                                                              *
* -- If you do not want to share these libraries across applications, you may  *
*    copy all files EXCEPT servlet.jar and jdbc.jar into your application's    *
*    WEB-INF/lib directory. Usually, servlet.jar and jdbc.jar are already      *
*    present in the app server's classpath and are provided in the Sparx       *
*    redists only to run Ant build files from the command line.                *
*                                                                              *
* -- IMPORTANT NOTE: Sparx has only been tested with Xerces and Xalan with     *
*    regards to XML parsing and XSLT transformations. Although Sparx uses JAXP *
*    and TrAX, the only libraries that have been certified for use are Xerces  *
*    and Xalan.                                                                *
********************************************************************************

Library                                 Ver        File                Source                                                            
--------------------------------------- ---------- ------------------- ----------------------------------------------------------------- 
Java JDBC API                           2.0        jdbc.jar            http://java.sun.com
Java Servlet API                        2.3        servlet.jar         http://java.sun.com
Apache Xalan                            2.4.0      xalan.jar           http://xml.apache.org/xalan-j
Apache Xalan JAXP/TrAX XML APIs         2.4.0      xml-apis.jar        http://xml.apache.org/xerces-j
Apache Xerces                           2.0.2      xerces.jar          http://xml.apache.org/xerces-j
Jakarta Ant                             1.5.0      ant.jar             http://jakarta.apache.org/ant
Jakarta Log4J                           1.2.6      log4j.jar           http://jakarta.apache.org/log4j/docs
Jakarta ORO                             2.0.4      oro.jar             http://jakarta.apache.org/oro
Jakarta Commons Logging                 1.0.2      commons-logging.jar http://jakarta.apache.org/commons
Jakarta Commons Jexl                    1.0 beta 1 commons-jexl.jar    http://jakarta.apache.org/commons
JUnit Testing Framework                 3.8        junit.jar           http://www.junit.org
Ostermiller Syntax Highlighting Library 1.1.1      syntax.jar          http://ostermiller.org/syntax
